Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.55,1:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite self\Nthat which you truly are is impersonal
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.55,1:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not an individual\Nseparate being
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.64,1:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that rises and falls\Nand has a name like David or something
