Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.69,1:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrating something by yourself\Nthose are the various techniques
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.69,1:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people use the finger technique\Nand with a little practice
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.69,1:18:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you get it\Nyou just keep practicing one thing after another
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.69,1:18:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get it\Nso these are sensitivities
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.01,1:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that you develop just by experience\Nyeah that's great
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.83,1:18:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,wow what a profound question\Nwe discovered that
