Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.12,1:19:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say\Nwell that can't be because of what I did
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.48,1:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,no it's not because of what you did\Nbut through that specific pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.92,1:19:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the science of mind\Nall those spiritual pathways
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.92,1:19:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,people have become healed\Nof every illness known to mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.92,1:19:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known people throughout the years\Nthat have recovered from every disease
