Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.95,1:19:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and all kinds of cancers\Nand heart attacks
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.95,1:19:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and diseases of every kind\Nfatal illnesses that have promptly recovered
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.95,1:19:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself have recovered from half a dozen\Nprogressively fatal illnesses
