Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.67,1:20:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,very interesting phenomena\Nclinically unique also
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.28,1:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,clinically unique\Na person with two levels of
