Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.78,1:21:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and that all that exists\Ndoes indeed move towards
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.78,1:22:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment\Nand that is the ultimate
