Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.32,1:25:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the books that make you go weak\Nyou go on this side of the room
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.32,1:25:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the books that make you go strong\Nyou put on that side of the room
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.32,1:25:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you leave them there for about a week\Nand amazing you see
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.32,1:25:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,oh wow\Nso the difference between truth
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.32,1:25:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and its misrepresentation\Nso the value of differentiating a true guru
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.32,1:25:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,from a false guru\Nwhich is one of the things I emphasize in my writings
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.57,1:25:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,always calibrate the level of truth of a speaker\Nbecause there are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.57,1:25:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there are gurus out there\Nthat are so clever
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.57,1:25:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they are ten times more clever than you are\Nand they collect the Cadillacs
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.57,1:25:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the money and the wealth\Nand the followers
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.57,1:25:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and they seem to be motivated by control\Nover large numbers of followers
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.57,1:25:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and so the\Nwhatchamacallits
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.86,1:25:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so the child of five speaking to someone\Ncould be an imaginary friend of childhood
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.86,1:25:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that's rather common in children\Nwho have an imaginary companion
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.86,1:26:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I would calibrate the level of it\Nit could also be
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.34,1:26:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking to a thing\Nspeaking to a thing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.34,1:26:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,well speaking to a thing\Nwould be either imaginary
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.34,1:26:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or could be hallucinated\Nand whether it's in evidence of childhood
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.34,1:26:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,mental illness or not you'd have to know\Nit could be just one of the imaginary
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.34,1:26:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,plaything of childhood\Nyou can use kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.12,1:26:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to assist any project you're up to\Nin self-improvement
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.15,1:26:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,any project\Nand I still find it to this day extremely useful
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.15,1:26:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in discovering things I never knew before\Ntoday right in front of this audience
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.15,1:26:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we discovered that\Nsomebody you would imagine would be at the pits of hell
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.72,1:26:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for eternity\Nis actually moving up in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.72,1:26:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,wow I didn't know that see\Nyou're learning things
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.72,1:27:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that change your whole paradigm of reality\Nand the evolution of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.36,1:27:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of young children remember previous lives\Nyou know about 15% of children
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.36,1:27:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,up to the age of what I forget\Nremember previous lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.36,1:27:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and unless you tell them to stop talking about that\Nit's imaginary and crazy
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.36,1:27:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,quite a few of them actually\Ndo literally remember
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.36,1:27:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as though the amnesia that's supposed to occur\Nas you reincarnate
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.36,1:27:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there's supposed to be an amnesia\Nand when do you recall previous lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.36,1:27:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,real significant and useful\Nwe asked that just this week
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.36,1:27:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,once you hit 600\Nit's really of academic interest
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.36,1:27:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,before 600\Nput 600 on
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.36,1:27:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it is possible to actually recall\Nand see the significance
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.36,1:27:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that who you are has been\Nin evolution for a great period of time
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.36,1:27:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I found that out\Nespecially about physical ailments
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.36,1:27:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,physical ailments\Ntend to be almost
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.36,1:27:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically precise\Nto something that's happened
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.36,1:28:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in some previous lifetime\Nyou don't have to believe any of this yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.97,1:28:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just say use kinesiology\Nand check it out yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.10,1:28:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can say\Nthis came from some other life
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.10,1:28:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,oh good what was it\Nso it's fun
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.13,1:28:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of it\Nrequires an open mind
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.08,1:28:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a true spiritual student then\Nhas an open mind
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.08,1:28:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and prays and says\Ndo God please reveal to me that which is useful to me
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.08,1:28:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I can understand\Nthat which I can integrate
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.08,1:28:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that which can benefit myself and others\Nand it's sort of like
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.08,1:28:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the third step in AA\Nwhere you totally surrender your life to
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.08,1:28:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,God as you understand him\Nand then you wait to see what happens
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.08,1:28:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and comes into your life\Nso at one point a thing is very significant
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.11,1:28:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and at another it's not\Nand what I'm telling you about today
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.11,1:28:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is covering a huge panorama of things\Nsome of which may or may not be significant
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.11,1:29:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at a given point in your life\Nyou may forget about
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.11,1:29:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or say they're absurd\Nand then one morning 10 years
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.11,1:29:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,now you wake up and you got it\NI got it happens to me
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.20,1:29:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as I drive down the highway all the time\NI'm driving down the highway and all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.20,1:29:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wow something is so obvious\NI'll say wow
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.20,1:29:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the same with jokes\NI don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.59,1:29:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard for me to stay serious in the world\Nand I have a great deal of time
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.59,1:29:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,trouble trying to stay serious\Nbecause everything presents itself in sort of a comical interpretation
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.59,1:29:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I keep saying\Nwhere in the world did that ever come from
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.04,1:29:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so life is a joy\Nand we'll just make one last statement
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.13,1:29:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll finish\Nwhere is the source of joy and happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.13,1:29:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is it in the future\Nin heaven
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.13,1:29:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the source of joy and happiness\Nawareness and enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.13,1:29:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in the joy of one's existence\Nin this very moment
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.13,1:29:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern\Nto be aware of the source of your existence
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.44,1:30:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,this instant\Nto be in a state of joy at all times
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.70,1:30:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,because that is the presence of God\Nthe presence of God is
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.70,1:30:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which you are\Nat this moment
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.73,1:30:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so the source of all joy\Njoy is not in the future
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.73,1:30:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not in the past\Nit's right in the awareness of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.73,1:30:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in this moment right now\Nthank you
